        article.am-article
            section.am-section
                :markdown
                    Hi there! I'm [Nicolas Bevacqua](/about#bio "About me"), a full-stack developer who loves his job. You can find me blogging on **Pony Foo**, just _click on the rainbows_ below. I _mostly_ write about JavaScript and the open web.

            p.am-center
                a.am-image-link(href='/blog', title='My blog at Pony Foo')
